    "Moreover, even in the case of Levels 4 and 5, some annotations had missing values, or the agreement between annotators was low.",
    "To overcome these limitations, future research should focus on developing a system that can automatically detect ball trajectories and hit points.",
    "This would significantly improve the accuracy and reliability of annotation data and provide researchers with more comprehensive insights into the mechanics of badminton strokes.",
    "Finally, our dataset focused on only two strokes, the forehand clear and backhand drive.",
    "Since our dataset's objective was to assess the quality of badminton strokes across all skill levels, from beginners to experts, we concentrated on these two fundamental strokes."
